name: CRUCIFIX
description:
Every person has a desire to soar like a bird in the sky. But the but many things shackled his desire so that he could not fly to where he wanted. Many bindings and restrictive such as rules, social demands, economics, culture, and the like. Even every second, time pierced the desire in him so that he could not fly freely. But as long as the passion in his eyes was not extinguished, there would definitely be something to force him out of it all, and fly high as he wished. when? Only time that can answer.

Made with Clip Studio Paint
JPEG, 7000x7000 pixel
300 DPI
